{"tid":2189841,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"警世 關於96出唔出","createTime":"2020-09-05T07:26:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T13:01:32.000Z","uid":173635,"like":36,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"a84e03440811fa53303b5343e441eb7b40f7df1e","tid":2189841,"uid":173635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:26:39.000Z","msg":"有冇發現每次有搞手出黎搞遊行搞集會就會有以下既聲音<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">1.個搞手好鬼/ 只係1x歲/ 個遊行好鬼</span><br />\n從來都唔係搞手舖好曬條路比你地班人行<br />\n唔通下下話曬啲詳情路線比狗聽咩<br />\n你地就年齡歧視人地一定諗野唔周全 <br />\n其實時間日期只不過係號召大家出黎自由發揮<br />\n真係冇一個人要為成個活動負上絕對責任<br />\n差在係大家願唔願意再行出黎 <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">2.出黎都係送頭</span><br />\n絕對明白 確實會有手足被捕<br />\n但送頭真係難聽過粗口<br />\n唔係每一個都承擔到風險<br />\n但風險既大小 <br />\n某程度上都取決於有幾多人出黎<br />\n如果成條彌敦道都係人<br />\n仲會唔會咁易比狗圍到捉到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">3.街頭戰線已冷卻 人少冇用</span><br />\n如果依家街頭戰線仲有當初地區遊行咁多人 你仲會唔會話冷卻 冇用？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VhiR8Hd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVhiR8Hd.jpg&h=0161c22e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fF1HvVE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfF1HvVE.jpg&h=44acbd5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實對家見到我地分化就最撚開心既 <br />\n我地每次手足搞活動都話有鬼有鬼唔好去<br />\n就正中佢下懷<br />\n亦係中左自己既圈套<br />\n就算自己人想去亦會因為咁而卻步<br />\n<br />\n我唔係話個活動唔會鬼 個搞手唔會鬼<br />\n只不過 講出黎分析再自決 <br />\n而唔係屌到成個連登都唔去<br />\n咁點樣令到件事鬼都變唔鬼<br />\n就係多人出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實已經超越左今次搞手假民主既問題<br />\n事實係過往都好少有票比你投出唔出<br />\n（我支持真民主既活動投票）<br />\n但今次係<br />\n你仲想唔想透過呢個街頭見既機會去表達同發聲<br />\n今次一過 大家都唔知等到幾時<br />\n（其實民陣去左邊？）<br />\n<br />\n所以係 <br />\n號召 然後 <span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">個人意志&gt;搞手意志</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果覺得任何人數形式街頭戰線都唔會有用既可以負皮然後上一頁<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係<br />\n希望大家可以認真反省下街頭戰線點先可以處理好分化問題<br />\n認真諗下96<br />\n認真諗下每一次街頭戰線既機會<br />\n<br />\n利申 真係好撚鐘意香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c6bf25b27d4f956646a25ed941d780c3773476d","tid":2189841,"uid":173635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:28:38.000Z","msg":"自推下 無人理就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0fbdd7d18510951c8fa7c8afd562bb794631b7d","tid":2189841,"uid":63338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:29:23.000Z","msg":"推，行街都唔比？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"039b821162cd0b0e89d8c395bf93c562ccdbfb96","tid":2189841,"uid":173635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:29:30.000Z","msg":"推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0572e9115258ca6d8e8400ed1fd9bb0bc667cf69","tid":2189841,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:29:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae5257916edd0b3ccbfcd0b751496de9d7ac1f0","tid":2189841,"uid":173635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:30:39.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以順便推番民陣出黎"},{"pid":"5c896605ccfa829ed58a218e8d41a6d9c243647d","tid":2189841,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:31:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d5fc42c17f7f1cee88f682abcc9e3c4c460deee6","tid":2189841,"uid":78222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:32:19.000Z","msg":"永遠遊行前都會有人屌搞手<br />\n笑人送頭活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8613f6b8b2e75a06fe8bd851b9bede84b11d0812","tid":2189841,"uid":173635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:34:09.000Z","msg":"推 再推"},{"pid":"4bdb8a982c6e3d357b83b8ff2de98a02e2de6bff","tid":2189841,"uid":173635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5fc42c17f7f1cee88f682abcc9e3c4c460deee6","tid":2189841,"uid":78222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:32:19.000Z","msg":"永遠遊行前都會有人屌搞手<br />\n笑人送頭活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:35:06.000Z","msg":"係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9372091c35980854c90f83d8f15a73b116f81806","tid":2189841,"uid":143682,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:48:40.000Z","msg":"巴打<br />\n互推"},{"pid":"0522f7eeddf1d4f6a7b5ad4bf831d7537971fbe8","tid":2189841,"uid":143682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:48:53.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"9dac40c2e5d74613af41e67595a1fa1b589f1170","tid":2189841,"uid":143682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:49:06.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"ea9c06a54ebe53a4ea58a2372e375230157b0acb","tid":2189841,"uid":173635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9372091c35980854c90f83d8f15a73b116f81806","tid":2189841,"uid":143682,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:48:40.000Z","msg":"巴打<br />\n互推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:49:32.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae36ef9ce59d3432ba47917b88921d233dd8822a","tid":2189841,"uid":173635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T08:01:36.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"6715b7ec620be380ce2d25fae83ca8be44dc2ec0","tid":2189841,"uid":167931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T08:02:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7e4f991ee2197c839d0666d3a2b1768b48780eb3","tid":2189841,"uid":248120,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T08:03:29.000Z","msg":"要出<br />\n但士可殺不可辱"},{"pid":"b65febbc4c27c9fee34114eee04582505dbcaad9","tid":2189841,"uid":182454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTim